# Chat App Realtime

![App Screenshot](image1.png)

## Overview

Chat App Realtime is a modern real-time chat application built with React, Firebase, and Appwrite. It allows users to engage in instant messaging, making communication fast and easy.

![Chat Interface](image2.png)

## Features

- Real-time chat: Communicate instantly with friends and family.
- User authentication: Securely register and log in to your account.
- User-friendly interface: Intuitive design for a seamless chatting experience.

![Authentication](image3.png)

## Getting Started

To get this project up and running, follow these steps:

1. Clone this repository:

   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/chat-app-realtime.git
2.Install dependencies:

  cd chat-app-realtime
  npm install

3.Start the development server:

  npm run dev

4.Open your web browser and navigate to http://localhost:3000 to access the chat app.

**Technologies Used**

React
Firebase
Appwrite
React Router
Vite
Tailwind CSS
DaisyUI

